These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, fanta, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, cricket, climbing, sailing
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person drinking soy-milk##2
4. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk         | soy-milk   | fanta | hot-chocolate       |
| Sport      | sailing | water-polo | climbing   | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, skydiving, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, italian, chinese, french
1. the french is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the italian##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the argentine##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | rock-climbing | skydiving | card-games |
| Nationality   | italian    | french   | argentine | chinese       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, zucchini, pineapple, cabbage
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish, italian
1. the polish is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the polish is between the indian and the person eating zucchini##2
3. the indian is on the far left##1
4. the italian is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person eating zucchini is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | spinach | zucchini   | pineapple  |
| Nationality   | indian | polish   | italian | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig, chinchilla, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cycling, soccer, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cycling is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rabbit   | turtle    | chinchilla       | guinea-pig   |
| Sport   | soccer | cricket | ice-hockey | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, almond-milk, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, drawing, rock-climbing
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea        | almond-milk | coffee  | milk |
| Hobby      | drawing | fishing  | rock-climbing | collecting    |

