.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep, gospel, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, tennis, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
4. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | gospel           | hip-hop | punk  |
| Sport         | swimming | snowboarding | surfing   | tennis |

