.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, soul, reggae, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, train, skateboard
1. the fan of soul is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the fan of disco is between the person driving the trike and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | soul | disco | reggae      |
| Transport     | train | trike    | car  | skateboard |

