.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, basketball, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, bus, boat
1. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person driving the bus##2
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | rowing | badminton | basketball     | cycling   |
| Transport   | bus   | quad-bike     | boat | skateboard |

