.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cauliflower, radish, blueberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, sailing, cricket, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person eating cauliflower and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | blueberry   | radish      | cauliflower   | spinach  |
| Sport   | snowboarding | sailing | cricket | skateboarding |

