.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, avocado, nectarine, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, family, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person eating avocado is between the person eating lettuce and the person eating cucumber##2
3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | cucumber     | avocado | lettuce   | nectarine        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | family   | romance | thriller |

