.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, baking, collecting, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, country, metal, reggae
1. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of country##1
5. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the fan of country is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | collecting | skydiving | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | metal          | country     | reggae  | soul     |

