2. the dancer is between the person watching family movies and the architect##2
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the architect is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | architect | dancer | engineer | project-manager     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | martial-arts    | family   | zombie |

