.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, russian, thai, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the turkish is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the thai is between the person driving the taxi and the russian##2
4. the turkish is on the right of the thai##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | russian | thai | turkish |
| Transport     | helicopter     | roller   | quad-bike | taxi  |

