.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, polish, dutch, thai
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird, rat, guinea-pig
1. the french is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the thai is the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the chinchilla and the polish##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | thai | polish | french | dutch |
| Pet           | rat  | guinea-pig  | bird | chinchilla      |

