.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, german, turkish, indian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, soccer, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the indian is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the pakistani and the turkish##2
5. the turkish is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | indian   | pakistani   | german | turkish |
| Sport         | biathlon | cycling | ice-hockey     | soccer    |

