.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, photography, gardening, board-games
4 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, hedgehog, dog
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the owner of the fish and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | gardening    | board-games     | hiking | photography |
| Pet     | mouse | dog | hedgehog       | fish     |

 